## Part 5 — How it all flows together (the full machine)

```
   YOU ASK A QUESTION
        |
        v
   LIBRARIAN grabs top-5 books   (clean books + maybe hidden fakes)
        |
        v
   [ RING 1 ]  block books that look fake at the door
        |
        v
   [ RING 2 ]  sort by trust, throw out the low-trust ones
        |
        v
   [ RING 3 ]  3 AIs vote.  Agree? -> answer.  Disagree? -> drop suspect, re-ask.
        |
        v
   TRUSTED ANSWER  +  a full report of what each ring did
```

Without shield: fakes win, ~90% wrong.
With shield: fakes caught, ~13% wrong (huge drop).

